{
  "text": "Let v lj (j \u00bc 1, 2, 3, 4, 5) and V l be the input velocities along l j and the general input velocity of the 5-DoF PM with 2U e . Let v, v, and V also be the linear, angular, and the general output velocities of m at o of the 5-DoF PM with 2U e . The formulae for solving V l and V of the 5-DoF PM with 2U e are derived [CITATION_1] as follows",
